Class TreeTableElementHolder

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dt.patterns.utils.TreeTableElementHolder

public class TreeTableElementHolder
extends java.lang.Object

This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtree representing an fnd:applicationsTreeTable.
